    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "旗牌",
        "曹真",
        "王朗",
        "郭淮"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王朗、郭淮、曹真同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹真",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉命西征，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王朗",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仗智谋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭淮",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大战蜀兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军师、将军请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王朗、郭淮",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（旗牌上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叩见元帅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你下书，那诸葛亮怎样回答？"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那诸葛言道：修书不及，照书行事。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（旗牌下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，军师！明日与蜀兵交战，必须定计而行，方可取胜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王朗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅明日出兵，务要严整队伍，大展旌旗。只用老夫一席言语，顺说孔明，管"
        },
        {
          "character": "王朗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫他不战而自降也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此就命郭将军点动人马，旌旗务要鲜明，军士务要强壮，刀枪明亮，鼓角整"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "齐。五更造饭，天明起兵，不得有误。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭淮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（郭淮下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹真",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "心中恼恨诸葛亮，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王朗",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "纵有机谋也无妨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹真",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "明日阵前来较量，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王朗",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "管叫他马前来归降。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹真、王朗同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
